      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a great car to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, it drives smoothly and is super comfortable. I\u2019ve kept up with the basics, so it's ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
