      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring a 7,900 RPM redline and six individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. The power is managed by a traditional 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip variable M differential. Maintenance is up to date with a recent double-VANOS overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension geometry remains true, providing excellent turn-in and communicative feedback through the steering rack. A mechanically sound example of an analog performance benchmark.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Regularly maintained. Clean interior and exterior. Mechanically sound. Title in hand.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect blend of performance and reliability. The exterior finish retains a deep luster, with only minor road peppering on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, and the original floor mats have been protected by all-weather liners since day one. Every feature\u2014from the panoramic sunroof to the advanced infotainment system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is sound, having followed a strict manufacturer-recommended service schedule with recent oil and filter changes. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that has been garaged throughout its ownership, making it an excellent choice for a discerning buyer seeking a dependable, high-quality ride without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, which exemplifies a superior standard of mechanical performance and aesthetic refinement. Having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection, this unit offers a commanding presence and an uncompromising driving experience. The interior remains remarkably well-preserved, complemented by a powertrain that delivers consistent, reliable output. This offering represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a high-caliber automotive asset that balances prestige with exceptional value.",
      "price": 34800.0,
