    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It runs great and has been well-maintained over the years\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks sharp on the road! It\u2019s got a few minor signs of love here and there, but it\u2019s solid, clean, and ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin, I think you'll really like how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
