      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a well-sorted E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65B40 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8. This high-revving powerplant delivers a linear power band peaking at an 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a Variable M Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system which provides versatile damping profiles. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive analysis of the rod bearings and replacement of the throttle actuators to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. The vehicle exhibits minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, but the subframe, VANOS system, and bushings are in robust working order, offering a visceral, analog driving experience that modern turbocharged platforms cannot replicate.",
